    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "You have two possible solution to control the number of the hits. The first solution is to use the widget [`HitsPerPageSelector` ](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/widgets/hitsPerPageSelector.html)it will display a select that lets the user control how many hits are displayed. But in case you don't want to let the user choose you can use the [`Configure`](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/widgets/configure.html) widget. \r\n\r\n```jsx\r\nsearch.addWidget(\r\n  instantsearch.widgets.configure({\r\n    hitsPerPage: 8,\r\n  })\r\n);\r\n```",
